name: Smoky Quartz Clover Briolette Necklace in Sterling Silver
description:
This smoky quartz necklace that features a dark gray faceted clover briolette. The delicate cable chain is sterling silver and closes with a lobster clasp. 

The necklace is 16.5 inches in total length. The smoky quartz bead measures 12x12 mm.

name: London Blue Topaz Dangle Earrings in Gold Filled
description:
Petite gemstone earrings with stacks of London blue topaz rondelles that dangle from handmade earwires. All of the metal components are gold filled.

The earrings measure 1.25 inches in total length. The topaz beads measure 2x3 mm. 

Gold-filled wire consists of a durable coating of gold bonded to a core of base metal. The gold layer will last decades given proper care.

name: Olive Quartz Briolette Pendant Necklace in Sterling Silver
description:
A wire wrapped olive quartz briolette pendant hangs from a delicate and ornate chain sterling silver chain.  This necklace is secured by a hand forged s-clasp. The earthy green quartz gemstone is eye clean and of excellent quality.

The necklace is 16 inches in total length. The briolette measures 6x8 mm and hangs 14 mm from the chain.

name: Lemon Citrine Bar Necklace in Sterling Silver
description:
This handmade necklace features a row of lemon yellow citrine rondelle beads at its centerpiece. The delicate sterling silver peanut chain closes with a lobster clasp. 

The necklace is 16 inches long. The center bar component measures 1.25 inches and is made of 3x4 mm beads.
